      .row
        .col-sm-12
          %h3.mt-3 Perforations as Card dividers
          %p Perforations were origionally designed as dividers between card body dividers. They can be placed within Cards, Panels or Fieldsets to divide them.

        .col-sm-4 
          .card.card-sard 
            .card-header Card
            .card-body
              %p 
                They can be placed between two card bodies
            .perf
            .card-body
              %p Like this
              %hr.black/
              %p Or within a .card-body 
              .perf
              %p like this
